Install Bash Update Script

curl -s https://raw.github.com/nandub/sublimetext-selfupdate/master/sltupdate > sltup

chmod 755 sltup

sudo cp -p sl2 /usr/local/bin

Update Sublime Text

sltup -b 2126 -l $HOME/devtools -BIPV 2

usage: sltup options

Sublime Text build installer.

OPTIONS:
   -h      Show this message
   -b      Specify build number
   -l      Location to installxi,. default: $HOME/Applications on Mac OS X or $HOME on Linux (TODO)
   -B      Install the Sublime Text TextMate Bundle
   -I      Install a better icon.
   -P      Install the Sublime Text Package Control Manager
   -V      Sublime Text build version, default 2.

